1
00:00:22,756 --> 00:00:26,827
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) [chuckling] I</i>
<i>will enshroud this world in</i>
<i>darkness.</i>

2
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:31,431
And now that the humans are no
longer capable of having dreams
beautiful enough...

3
00:00:31,532 --> 00:00:35,836
to make the Golden Crystal
shine, there's nothing you can
do to stop me!

4
00:00:39,439 --> 00:00:41,441
[gasps] Chibi Moon?

5
00:00:41,508 --> 00:00:42,475
Listen!

6
00:00:44,310 --> 00:00:47,380
I'm calling on everyone in the
world who possesses beautiful
dreams to lend me your power!

7
00:00:47,614 --> 00:00:50,851
So please! I need you all to
pray with me, right now!

8
00:00:51,652 --> 00:00:54,788
Moon Crisis Power!

9
00:00:55,221 --> 00:01:08,374
Moon Crisis Power!

10
00:01:13,580 --> 00:01:17,383
It can't be! The Golden Crystal
is shinning!

11
00:01:18,384 --> 00:01:23,824
[screaming]

12
00:03:02,836 --> 00:03:07,273
<i>(Usagi) "Dreams Forever: Fill</i>
<i>the Heavens with Light."</i>

13
00:03:52,719 --> 00:03:55,656
[grunting]

14
00:03:55,756 --> 00:03:56,557
[gasps]

15
00:04:01,668 --> 00:04:03,436
Chibi Moon!

16
00:04:14,748 --> 00:04:15,448
What?

17
00:04:16,182 --> 00:04:17,017
<i>(Sailor Moon) What's happening?</i>

18
00:04:18,018 --> 00:04:19,720
[gasps] Chibi Moon!

19
00:04:22,422 --> 00:04:24,024
[grunting]

20
00:04:25,025 --> 00:04:27,794
[grunting]

21
00:04:36,570 --> 00:04:41,808
[grunting]

22
00:04:42,776 --> 00:04:45,411
[grunting]

23
00:04:45,712 --> 00:04:51,384
[heavy breathing]

24
00:04:51,818 --> 00:04:52,719
Hmph!

25
00:05:03,770 --> 00:05:07,473
[heavy breathing]

26
00:05:07,574 --> 00:05:11,512
<i>This whole place is being pulled</i>
<i>upwards, toward the New Moon!</i>

27
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:20,687
<i>It can't be!</i>

28
00:05:22,455 --> 00:05:25,759
<i>The force that once sealed me</i>
<i>inside that darkness has started</i>
<i>to take effect again.</i>

29
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:30,631
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) Could the</i>
<i>power of this little girl's</i>
<i>dream be the cause?</i>

30
00:05:39,706 --> 00:05:49,850
[heavy breathing]

31
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:51,051
[gasps]

32
00:05:51,151 --> 00:05:58,692
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) [screaming in</i>
<i>horror</i>]

33
00:06:02,803 --> 00:06:06,973
[Heavy Breathing]

34
00:06:16,817 --> 00:06:22,055
No...Is this supposed to be me?

35
00:06:22,656 --> 00:06:23,924
[grunts]

36
00:06:27,193 --> 00:06:33,199
Stay away! Don't come any
closer, you of the White Moon.

37
00:06:34,267 --> 00:06:35,569
[gasps]

38
00:06:40,907 --> 00:06:46,547
I see. I can see now that you
are the Princess of the White
Moon reincarnated.

39
00:06:46,847 --> 00:06:49,015
You know who I am?

40
00:06:49,115 --> 00:06:51,685
You don't remember
me, do you?

41
00:06:51,852 --> 00:06:55,055
I used to watch the goings‐on in
your kingdom.

42
00:06:55,188 --> 00:06:57,858
And how it did fill my heart
with envy...

43
00:06:57,958 --> 00:07:02,035
to watch the white moon shinning
there with a light that promised
happiness.

44
00:07:03,369 --> 00:07:11,244
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) Do you know</i>
<i>how I ended up a solitary queen,</i>
<i>living alone on a tiny asteroid?</i>

45
00:07:13,714 --> 00:07:18,619
<i>I too was once a queen,</i>
<i>surrounded by many retainers.</i>

46
00:07:18,719 --> 00:07:21,622
Queen Nehalennia! Queen
Nehalennia! Beautiful!

47
00:07:21,722 --> 00:07:24,658
You look beautiful as ever,
Queen Nehalennia.

48
00:07:24,891 --> 00:07:27,594
[fawning over Queen]

49
00:07:27,794 --> 00:07:30,631
How may I be of service, my
beautiful Queen?

50
00:07:30,797 --> 00:07:34,300
[adoring cheers]

51
00:07:35,301 --> 00:07:39,105
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) All my people</i>
<i>adored their beautiful queen.</i>

52
00:07:39,239 --> 00:07:44,244
<i>And like them, I too thought</i>
<i>that my beauty would last</i>
<i>forever.</i>

53
00:07:46,747 --> 00:07:51,184
Until one day, my mirror showed
me the horrible truth.

54
00:07:52,018 --> 00:07:56,623
Oh, mirror, mirror, reveal to
me my beautiful future, I
beg you.

55
00:07:56,757 --> 00:08:00,326
My dream is to stay young and
beautiful like this forever.

56
00:08:00,426 --> 00:08:04,037
Won't you please show me what
lies ahead for my dream?

57
00:08:05,772 --> 00:08:06,607
[gasps]

58
00:08:09,142 --> 00:08:10,276
[screams]

59
00:08:10,677 --> 00:08:13,947
What? What was that? [gasps]

60
00:08:16,382 --> 00:08:17,618
[gasps]

61
00:08:19,352 --> 00:08:21,287
[gasps]

62
00:08:21,955 --> 00:08:24,357
<i>(Queen Nehalennia) [gasps] No!</i>

63
00:08:30,797 --> 00:08:32,866
Is this how I'll end up?

64
00:08:32,999 --> 00:08:36,970
[screams]

65
00:08:37,738 --> 00:08:39,305
It's...hideous!

66
00:08:41,141 --> 00:08:47,213
<i>(Zirconia) Always remember not</i>
<i>to forget. A child's dream is a</i>
<i>dream they should never get.</i>

67
00:08:47,313 --> 00:08:55,656
<i>(Zirconia) Always remember not</i>
<i>to forget. A child's dream is a</i>
<i>dream they should never get.</i>

68
